{"tid":1964340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識玩鬥獸棋？","createTime":"2020-04-08T18:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T19:19:14.000Z","uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0209ed12ae11977d108ad2e821f3c91818046c49","tid":1964340,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"WFH期間，屋企細路漏我捉棋<br />\n之前買落左副鬥獸棋<br />\n我就一向冇捉，唔識捉是但捉，<br />\n<br />\n好啦，象棋都唔可以行落河，<br />\n個仔居然行隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左落去<br />\n咁我問：咁都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢：咩唔得！你睇下點玩先同我玩啦<br />\n我：有冇聽過蛇吞象？我用隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食左佢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢：吓？鼠邊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天敵啊<br />\n我：咩唔得啊 你行得落河又得<br />\n我隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太餓鐘意食咩就食咩囉<br />\n<br />\n然後佢就嬲左我唔同我玩啦<br />\n其實有咩係可以食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n另外呀，可唔可以當盲棋玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaedf7f49b9b1cba9ef76464819a93fe23982b16","tid":1964340,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"我諗住聽朝同佢捉象棋，<br />\n成堆棋擺晒落河<br />\n話full team都識游水<br />\n然後就可以順利捉贏佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c68dcf8f3458014a48ea5e79bb57b047f0ca93a","tid":1964340,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"冇人識捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼠邊鼠係天敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a891dfecbc140b1c9fa0f9888526d582953bbd","tid":1964340,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58dffc3fed3a460376f28ec5f146e285a77d2de0","tid":1964340,"uid":317345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:19:14.000Z","msg":"玩人殺哂"}]}